          "paperId": "3641755382104064",
          "source": "《电工技术基础与技能》综合练习（七）45分钟专题训练（原卷版+)",
          "year": 2024,
          "difficulty": 0.65,
          "stem": "<div class=\"qml-stem\"><p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">电阻</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">R1=4</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">Ω和</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">R2=3</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">Ω串联于电源电压</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">V</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">上，则其功率比为（</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'\" qml-space-size=\"3\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">）</span></p><div class=\" qml-og\"><table class=\"qml-og\" style=\"width:100%\"><tr><td>A.&nbsp;<span class=\"qml-op\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">3</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">∶</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">4</span></span></td><td>B.&nbsp;<span class=\"qml-op\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">4</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">∶</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">3</span></span></td><td>C.&nbsp;<span class=\"qml-op\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">9</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">∶</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">6</span></span></td><td colspan=\"1\">D.&nbsp;<span class=\"qml-op\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">16</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">∶</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">9</span></span></td></tr></table></div></div>",
          "answer": "<div class=\"qml-answer\"><span class=\"qml-an-sq\"><span class=\"qml-an qml-isop\">B</span></span></div>",
          "explanation": "<div class=\"qml-explanation\"><div class=\"qml-seg\" seg-name=\"详解\">【详解】<p style=\"text-align:justify;word-break:break-word;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">在串联电路中，电流是处处相等的。因此，当电阻</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">R1</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">和</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">R2</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">串联在电源电压</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">V</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">上时，通过它们的电流是相同的。利用功率的公式来计算每个电阻的功率。功率</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">P</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">的公式为：</span><math latex=\"$P=I^{2}R$\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mi>P</mi><mo>=</mo><msup><mi>I</mi><mn>2</mn></msup><mi>R</mi></math><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">由于</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">R1</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">和</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">R2</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">的电流相同，我们可以直接比较它们的电阻值来确定功率比。根据题目，</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">R1=4</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">和</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">R2=3</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">，所以它们的功率比为：</span><math latex=\"$\\frac{P1}{P2}=\\frac{I^{2}R1}{I^{2}R2}=\\frac{R1}{R2}=\\frac{4}{3}$\"><mrow><mfrac><mrow><mi>P</mi><mn>1</mn><mtext>​</mtext></mrow><mrow><mi>P</mi><mn>2</mn></mrow></mfrac><mo>=</mo><mfrac><mrow><msup><mi>I</mi><mn>2</mn></msup><mi>R</mi><mn>1</mn></mrow><mrow><msup><mi>I</mi><mn>2</mn></msup><mi>R</mi><mn>2</mn></mrow></mfrac><mo>=</mo><mfrac><mrow><mi>R</mi><mn>1</mn><mtext>​</mtext></mrow><mrow><mi>R</mi><mn>2</mn></mrow></mfrac><mo>=</mo><mfrac><mn>4</mn><mn>3</mn></mfrac><mtext>​</mtext></mrow></math><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\"> </span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">因此，电阻</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">R1</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">和</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">R2</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">的功率比是</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">4:3</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">。即电阻</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">R1</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">和</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">R2</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">的功率比为</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">4:3</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">。故选</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">B</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">。</span></p></div></div>",
