          "stem": "<div class=\"qml-stem\"><p style=\"text-align:justify;word-break:break-word;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">一个闭合电路中，总电流是</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">2A</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">，总电阻是</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">5Ω</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">，求端电压是多少？（</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'\" qml-space-size=\"3\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">）</span></p><div class=\" qml-og\"><table class=\"qml-og\" style=\"width:100%\"><tr><td>A.&nbsp;<span class=\"qml-op\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">5V</span></span></td><td>B.&nbsp;<span class=\"qml-op\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">7V</span></span></td><td>C.&nbsp;<span class=\"qml-op\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">8V</span></span></td><td colspan=\"1\">D.&nbsp;<span class=\"qml-op\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">10V</span></span></td></tr></table></div></div>",
