          "source": "第一章 第三节  闭合电路欧姆定律",
          "year": 2025,
          "difficulty": 0.65,
          "stem": "<div class=\"qml-stem\"><p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">一块太阳能电池板，测得它的开路电压为</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">800mV</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">，短路电流为</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">40mA</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">，若将该电池板与一个阻值为</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">20Ω</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">的电阻器连成一闭合电路，则它的端电压是（</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'\" qml-space-size=\"3\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">）</span></p><div class=\" qml-og\"><table class=\"qml-og\" style=\"width:100%\"><tr><td>A.&nbsp;<span class=\"qml-op\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">0.1V</span></span></td><td>B.&nbsp;<span class=\"qml-op\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">0.2V</span></span></td><td>C.&nbsp;<span class=\"qml-op\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">0.3V</span></span></td><td colspan=\"1\">D.&nbsp;<span class=\"qml-op\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">0.4V</span></span></td></tr></table></div></div>",
          "answer": "<div class=\"qml-answer\"><span class=\"qml-an-sq\"><span class=\"qml-an qml-isop\">D</span></span></div>",
          "explanation": "<div class=\"qml-explanation\"><div class=\"qml-seg\" seg-name=\"详解\">【详解】<p style=\"text-align:justify;word-break:break-word;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">因电路的开路电压等于电源电动势，即</span><math latex=\"$E=800\\mathrm{mV}$\"><mrow><mi>E</mi><mo>=</mo><mn>800</mn><mtext>mV</mtext></mrow></math><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">，短路电流</span><math latex=\"$I_{\\mathrm{短}}=\\frac{E}{r}$\"><mrow><msub><mi>I</mi><mi mathvariant=\"normal\">短</mi></msub><mo>=</mo><mfrac><mi>E</mi><mi>r</mi></mfrac></mrow></math><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">，则</span><math latex=\"$r=\\frac{E}{I_{\\mathrm{短}}}=\\frac{800\\mathrm{mV}}{40\\mathrm{mA}}=20\\Upomega$\"><mrow><mi>r</mi><mo>=</mo><mfrac><mi>E</mi><mrow><msub><mi>I</mi><mi mathvariant=\"normal\">短</mi></msub></mrow></mfrac><mo>=</mo><mfrac><mrow><mn>800</mn><mtext>mV</mtext></mrow><mrow><mn>40</mn><mtext>mA</mtext></mrow></mfrac><mo>=</mo><mn>20</mn><mi mathvariant=\"normal\">Ω</mi></mrow></math><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">。若将该电池板与一个阻值为</span><math latex=\"$20\\Upomega$\"><mrow><mn>20</mn><mi mathvariant=\"normal\">Ω</mi></mrow></math><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">的电阻器连成一闭合电路，则电路中的电流为</span><math latex=\"$I=\\frac{E}{R+r}=\\frac{800\\mathrm{mV}}{20\\Upomega +20\\Upomega }=0.02\\mathrm{A}$\"><mrow><mi>I</mi><mo>=</mo><mfrac><mi>E</mi><mrow><mi>R</mi><mo>+</mo><mi>r</mi></mrow></mfrac><mo>=</mo><mfrac><mrow><mn>800</mn><mtext>mV</mtext></mrow><mrow><mn>20</mn><mi mathvariant=\"normal\">Ω</mi><mo>+</mo><mn>20</mn><mi mathvariant=\"normal\">Ω</mi></mrow></mfrac><mo>=</mo><mn>0.02</mn><mtext>A</mtext></mrow></math><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">，则它的端电压</span><math latex=\"$U=IR=0.02\\times 20\\mathrm{V}=0.4\\mathrm{V}$\"><mrow><mi>U</mi><mo>=</mo><mi>I</mi><mi>R</mi><mo>=</mo><mn>0.02</mn><mo>×</mo><mn>20</mn><mtext>V</mtext><mo>=</mo><mn>0.4</mn><mtext>V</mtext></mrow></math><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">。故</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">D</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">正确。</span></p></div></div>",
