          "stem": "<div class=\"qml-stem\"><p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">电路如图所示，</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">E</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">是电源电动势，</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">r</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">是电源内阻，若</span><math latex=\"$\\frac{1}{R_{P}}< \\frac{1}{R_{1}}+\\frac{1}{r}，$\"><mfrac><mrow><mn>1</mn></mrow><mrow><msub><mrow><mi>R</mi></mrow><mrow><mi>P</mi></mrow></msub></mrow></mfrac><mo>&lt;</mo><mfrac><mrow><mn>1</mn></mrow><mrow><msub><mrow><mi>R</mi></mrow><mrow><mn>1</mn></mrow></msub></mrow></mfrac><mo>+</mo><mfrac><mrow><mn>1</mn></mrow><mrow><mi>r</mi></mrow></mfrac><mo>，</mo></math><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">当</span><math latex=\"$R_{P}$\"><msub><mrow><mi>R</mi></mrow><mrow><mi>P</mi></mrow></msub></math><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">调大时，</span><math latex=\"$R_{P}$\"><msub><mrow><mi>R</mi></mrow><mrow><mi>P</mi></mrow></msub></math><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">获得的功率将（</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'\" qml-space-size=\"3\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">）</span></p><p style=\"text-align: left;\"><img  height=\"93\" src=\"https://img.xkw.com/dksih/QBM/2026/1/12/3926966974472192/3927600946765824/STEM/35bfd5703d264069956987fefef5f86e.png\" width=\"118\" /></p><div class=\" qml-og\"><table class=\"qml-og\" style=\"width:100%\"><tr><td>A.&nbsp;<span class=\"qml-op\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">变大</span></span></td><td>B.&nbsp;<span class=\"qml-op\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">变小</span></span></td><td>C.&nbsp;<span class=\"qml-op\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">不变</span></span></td><td colspan=\"1\">D.&nbsp;<span class=\"qml-op\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">无法确定</span></span></td></tr></table></div></div>",
