          "explanation": "<div class=\"qml-explanation\"><div class=\"qml-seg\" seg-name=\"详解\">【详解】<p style=\"\"><span>断开RP求开路电压UOC ：UOC=</span><math latex=\"$U_{OC}=\\frac{E}{R_{1}+r}\\times R_{1}$\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><msub><mi>U</mi><mrow><mi>O</mi><mi>C</mi></mrow></msub><mo>=</mo><mfrac><mi>E</mi><mrow><msub><mi>R</mi><mn>1</mn></msub><mo>+</mo><mi>r</mi></mrow></mfrac><mo>×</mo><msub><mi>R</mi><mn>1</mn></msub></math></p><p style=\"\"><span>等效电阻为</span><span style=\"\">R0​ =</span><span>R1//r</span></p><p style=\"\"><span style=\"\"><span>根据</span><span>最大功率传输定理</span><span>，当负载电阻 RP​ 大于等效内阻 R0​ 时，随着 RP​ 的增大，负载获得的功率会</span><span>减小</span><span>。</span></span></p><p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span>因为</span><img  height=\"45\" src=\"https://img.xkw.com/dksih/QBM/editorImg/2026/2/25/35198bd2-326a-4d53-a2b5-84a51ec60d92.png\" width=\"121\" /></p><p style=\"\"><span>所以</span><span style=\"\">RP​ 大于等效内阻 R0</span></p><p style=\"\"><span>所以选B</span></p></div></div>",
